====[https://www.osapublishing.org/abstract.cfm?URI=ao-15-7-1871 A. Rabl, “Solar concentrators with maximal concentration for cylindrical absorbers,” Applied Optics, vol. 15, no. 7, p. 1871, Jul. 1976. doi: 10.1364/AO.15.001871]====

